<div class="carousel-item">
  <img src="{{ asset('images/' ~ '3.png') }}" class="d-block w-100" alt="banner">
  <div class="carousel-caption d-none">
    <h5 class="text-center">"かいぞく の おう に</h5>
    <h5 class="text-center">なる わ なる"</h5>
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
      <p class="text-wrap text-break">arittakeno yume o kakiatsume sagashi mono sagashini yuku no sa one piece rashinban nante jyutai no moto netsu ni ukasare kaji o toru no sa hokori ka butteta takara no chizu mo tashikameta no nara densetsu jyanai!</p>
    </div>
